snippet.title: Room 54 - Teaser
snippet.description:
first teaser of Room 54, our demo will come out in semptember end, be ready!

http://www.Room54-thegame.com

Twitter:            https://twitter.com/Room54Thegame

Facebook:       https://www.facebook.com/Room54/

IndieDB:           http://www.indiedb.com/games/room54

Room54 is a first person horror/survival videogame for pc,mac,linux users currently under development with CryEngine 5, the gameplay is based on investigating, solve enigma and survive  in an immersive horror atmosphere followed by an high dose of tension throughout the game.
